            <title>[HBASE-2554] Provide single method for returning a collection of HColumnDescriptors from an HTableDescriptor</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-2554</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;At &lt;a href=&quot;http://hadoop.apache.org/hbase/docs/r0.20.4/api/org/apache/hadoop/hbase/HTableDescriptor.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://hadoop.apache.org/hbase/docs/r0.20.4/api/org/apache/hadoop/hbase/HTableDescriptor.html&lt;/a&gt;, we currently have both HColumnDescriptor[] getColumnFamilies() and Collection&amp;lt;HColumnDescriptor&amp;gt; getFamilies(); perhaps only one is needed?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
